Teste 1.query:
Select distinct 
         
       sku_cod_terceiro                           AS MATERIAL
       ,item_id_item                              AS ITEM_WMS
       ,item_id_sku                               AS SKU_WMS
       ,sku_nome                                  AS DESCRICAO
       ,item_tipo_unl                             AS UNL
       ,sku_id_setor                              AS DEPT
       ,sku_peso_unitario_kg                      AS PESO_KG
       ,item_altura                               AS ALTURA
       ,item_largura                              AS LARGURA
       ,item_comprimento                          AS COMPR
       ,item_volume_m3                            AS M3
       

from `b2w-bee-analytics.raw_wms_tables_current.wlasa_sku`sku

       LEFT JOIN b2w-bee-analytics.raw_wms_tables.wlasa_item  AS i
        ON item_cod_terceiro = sku_cod_terceiro
        AND DATE(i.process_time) <= CURRENT_DATE 

where item_tipo_unl <> ' '
AND sku_id_setor > '0'
